@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@
+# Pruned
+
+- **Sort-key registry / dict-of-key-functions / strategy base class.** Rejected:
+  only one real variant (`text`) is required now; need >=2 before abstracting.
+  `choices=["text"]` + one conditional is equally extensible without the layer.
+- **Sorting inside store.load / a new store function.** Rejected: ordering is a
+  list-command presentation concern; keeping it out of the store leaves the
+  insertion-order baseline contract untouched.
