@@ -0,0 +1,9 @@
+# Corridor: E3-B-3-sort-list
+
+Add `--sort text` to the `list` command. Sort is a presentation concern in
+`cmd_list`; the store stays insertion-ordered. Only the `text` key is required
+now, so no key registry / strategy object — a single `choices`-validated arg
+plus one conditional. Adding `id`/`created` later is a one-line change.
+
+## Paths
+- cli_notes/cli.py
